Reliability and Fault Tolerance

The system has been designed with industrial deployment in mind. Several mechanisms ensure operational continuity:

Network Failure Protection

Attendance continues normally even without internet connectivity.

Storage Redundancy

Every attendance entry is written to both internal flash memory and an SD card.

Automatic Log Recovery

If cloud uploads fail, unsent logs remain stored locally and are retransmitted later.

Time Synchronization Recovery

The RTC maintains accurate time independently and periodically resynchronizes with NTP servers when available.

Auto-Reconnection

Wi-Fi connectivity is automatically restored whenever possible.

